Hello!
In this application you can download mods for MCPE, which will add a lot of cool and powerful weapons to make the game process even more interesting and dynamic. Now you can arrange real battles with your friends.

Soon, the application will have a lot of cool mods, don't miss it!

To download the mod you like:

1. Click on the “DOWNLOAD” button, in the main menu;

2. Choose the mod you want to download;

3. Download the mod by clicking on the “LINK” button (you will go to the Google Disk, which contains the mod, for download);

4. Install the mod, according to the instructions that you will find by clicking the “GUIDE” button, in the main menu.
